overview: Having been framed for murder, the half-breed Joe Bearclaws (Douglas Kennedy) escapes from jail and Ranger Steve Howard (Monte Hale) goes after him. He catches up with him in the Cherokee Strip where he has no authority. Joe is then framed for another murder and this time Steve knows he is innocent and goes after the real killer.
tagline: MONTE'S GUNS ROAR A DEADLY CHALLENGE TO CHAMPION A DESPERATE CAUSE!
title: Ranger of Cherokee Strip
